{"tid":557546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又一單】疑避交通警追截　私家車粉嶺公路翻側兩死","createTime":"2018-02-11T12:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T13:05:50.000Z","uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"820b034457088fecaa04c3932272d010f3463bfe","tid":557546,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8wkOG-hNuVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8wkOG-hNuVA&d=Vm%2BvChM2uigGI6EO2m2Xkk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=60e676fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8wkOG-hNuVA</a><br />\n今日（11日）下午5時35分，粉嶺公路往九龍方向近九龍坑發生奪命交通意外。一輛涉觸犯交通規例的私家車，為避開交通警追截，於公路上飛馳並失控翻側，車上司機當場死亡，男乘客則滿臉鮮血昏迷送院，其後證實不治。據指，事發時私家車在路上左穿右插，期間撞毀另外三輛私家車，造成其餘4人受傷，當中包括一名電單車交通警。<br />\n<br />\n一段「車Cam」片段流出，顯示當時一輛高速的銀色私家車失控拐彎，撞向前面車速不高的車輛，導致其擋風玻璃破裂。消息指，警察電單車於新界環迴公路錦綉花園開始追截涉事私家車。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署於下午5時54分宣佈，因交通意外，粉嶺公路往大埔方向近馬會道的部份行車線現已封閉。駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。現時在粉嶺公路往大埔方向的車龍龍尾已到粉嶺港鐵站。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/204627_35318f004974225653bff0bcf9899374.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F204627_35318f004974225653bff0bcf9899374.png&h=496342f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/204628_43bd850006917245dc26c66bda5c2133.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F204628_43bd850006917245dc26c66bda5c2133.png&h=381f00e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/204628_339a19eaebecae6efa83323c21f70f53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F204628_339a19eaebecae6efa83323c21f70f53.png&h=5c71278a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba2cb0595fdd0872f3472b18ff808fe3c3577ec1","tid":557546,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點都好<br />\n死黑警"},{"pid":"bebfae62f03c8acb9555a8b5dc0c5f4efea66bbb","tid":557546,"uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/210447_778a04f59f9426a502b75ad275d06bce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F210447_778a04f59f9426a502b75ad275d06bce.png&h=2ea3a648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男乘客送院後證實不治。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/210448_38e1872320142a5c8deab9695f489d6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F210448_38e1872320142a5c8deab9695f489d6b.png&h=1c80faf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名男子當場死亡"}]}